# Projection-engine proof 3 (P3a): recency drives scale + spiral ordinal.
# size-by-recency grows the newest-visited node and shrinks the oldest; the
# Spiral then seats newest-first (freshest at the center, age spiralling
# outward) and fits the view so the whole spiral frames. Offline (mere://
# sample ring). Reopening alpha after gamma is deliberate: `visit()` stamps
# the existing node through the graph delta, so alpha becomes the newest
# score ordinal rather than merely moving focus. Fresh profile.
settle 30
key escape

open mere://alpha
settle 10
open mere://gamma
settle 30
open mere://alpha
settle 10
capture 01_uniform_force

act Toggle size-by-recency
settle 20
capture 02_recency_sizes

act Layout: Spiral
settle 20
act Fit view
settle 20
act Save session
settle 5
capture 03_recency_spiral

log projection proof 3 persisted score complete
